{"tid":82962,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"關於media 入行","createTime":"2017-01-16T11:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T11:55:48.000Z","uid":71369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"514a8e5b77a34668e0603c60ef87f97c8a0bad70","tid":82962,"uid":71369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:05:47.000Z","msg":"想請問有冇方法可以入到行？最想入電影，production house 個類<br />\n我副修係multi media, 都識剪片影相，見過post 話入tvb 做pa 比較易，但Jobsdb 暫時未見到有recruitment ，所以唔知點入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想問下大家意見係咪再讀啲短course 會有用啲？我上網睇過好似唔多，有冇好介紹？或者有冇啲剪片freelance 做下儲下經歷？<br />\n萬分感謝！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288e8b64ae9e53fa66a8abc7e8ef60bc0c1ba98d","tid":82962,"uid":33896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:14:58.000Z","msg":"電影行頭,撚就啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f4b1c1273a83a233c6854c94705ce784852ee7","tid":82962,"uid":71369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電影行頭,撚就啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我微電影，mv 所有都好有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c05fb97b3f27ff0f5125bd397140f1c25e18f1d7","tid":82962,"uid":33896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T14:46:42.000Z","msg":"點唔撚透既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你咪去試下囉<br />\n一個搵唔到錢既行頭<br />\n你都養唔到自己幾耐"},{"pid":"5952ba3a13fb53a80c1f028eea1fe1e662cc1db6","tid":82962,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T14:50:53.000Z","msg":"想入TVB自己上去官網睇,365日都請人,但小撚心做三個月都唔夠喊住走返出來"},{"pid":"20880bac34b40d69b33b4dcd169b982